//vue is used for interactive webapps
//NON-VUE:
//address will send a request to the server 
//then the server will handle the request and sends back the html page
//SO... browser is making new requests on every click to the page

//VUE:
//every click on the website will not go to the server
//instead it gets sent to VUE and does what it needs
//called- single page application(only one html page)

